active: boolean or Closure, optional, whether this menu item is in active state (currently selected). When using a closure, its signature should be function ($item, $hasActiveChild, $isItemActive, $widget). Closure must return true if item should be marked as active, otherwise - false. If a menu item is active, its CSS class will be appended with $activeCssClass. If this option is not set, the menu item will be set active automatically when the current request is triggered by url. For more details, please refer to isItemActive().
